>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">h₀</span> : <span class=\"fn\">∀ (<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ι</span>), <span class=\"fn\">0</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#LE.le\">≤</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">w</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">h₁</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/BigOperators/Finprod.html#finsum\">∑ᶠ</a> (<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ι</span>)<a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/BigOperators/Finprod.html#finsum\">,</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">w</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span></span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">1</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hz</span> : <span class=\"fn\">∀ (<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ι</span>), <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">w</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Ne\">≠</a> <span class=\"fn\">0</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">z</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Membership.mem\">∈</a> <span class=\"fn\">s</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/BigOperators/Finprod.html#finsum\">∑ᶠ</a> (<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ι</span>)<a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/BigOperators/Finprod.html#finsum\">,</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">w</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HSMul.hSMul\">•</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">z</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span></span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Membership.mem\">∈</a> <span class=\"fn\">s</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A version of `Convex.sum_mem` for `finsum`s. If `s` is a co